    "client_msg_id": "6cdab3e5-56af-492d-8e3b-d5b9bc6da9a3",
    "type": "message",
    "text": "I learned about this group from the Future of Programming unsession at strangeloop. I'm interested in ways that make computing more accessible for everyone. I'm working on a DSL for reactive pixel art called Pikov <https://github.com/google/pikov> Currently the reactive behavior is just Markov chains, but I'm interested in ways to incorporate transitions based on events in a natural visual programming interface.",
